ygData.subject: mindless and idle thoughts 'cuz I'm bored..
ygData.msgSnippet: Isn t it fun when you go to West COmmons and kill Militia Colin and Volin  so many times that, the Guards in North Ro, East commons and West Commons
ygData.messageBody:
Isn't it fun when you go to West COmmons and kill Militia Colin and Volin
<whatever> so many times that, the Guards in North Ro, East commons and West
Commons will now kill you? <grin> Well they don't scowl at me, ready to
attack.. they look at me threateningly.. but when I just walked by the first
guard in North Ro that stay at the three way intersection near the desert,
he came after me and killed me... bleh.. back to half way to level for the
4th time this level.. guess I won't be walking the streets of Freeport any
time soon... ah.. the sewers life for me... not that I ever go into Freeport
much, being a Dark-elf.. just annoying that now I can't go towards or near
the Inns in east commonlands at all now.. not that the Innkeepers much like
me anyway.. but at least I could sit by the trees near the Inn's..
anyways... don't suppose anyone happens to have any information on Vampiric
Embrace yet as to what it now does? Ok.. I'm done rambling now...
